    <detaileddescription>
<para>Terminates the thread immediately, leaving <computeroutput>exited( _Term_)</computeroutput> as result-state for <ref refid="classthread__join_22" kindref="compound">thread_join/2</ref> If the thread has the attribute <computeroutput>detached</computeroutput> <computeroutput>true</computeroutput> it terminates, but its exit status cannot be retrieved using <ref refid="classthread__join_22" kindref="compound">thread_join/2</ref> making the value of <emphasis>Term</emphasis> irrelevant The Prolog stacks and C-thread are reclaimed </para>
    </detaileddescription>
